[Nouns] detractor, reprover; censor, censurer; cynic, critic, caviler, carper, word-catcher, frondeur; barracker.
defamer, backbiter, slanderer, Sir Benjamin Backbite, lampooner, satirist, traducer, libeler, caluminiator, dawplucker, Thersites; Zoilus; good-natured friend [satirically]; reviler, vituperator, castigator; shrew [more]; muckraker.
disapprover, laudator temporis acti [Horace].
